claim.claim-text:
1. A method for selectively transmitting a distress signal from a hand-held electronic device in a time of distress, the method comprising:
during the time of distress, impacting an impact surface of the device against another surface, the impact surface of the device not being subjected to an impact during other operation of the device;
generating electrical energy resulting from an impact force applied to the impact surface of the device;
providing the generated power to a transmitter in the device; and
transmitting the distress signal from the transmitter.
